schools.name: Imogene Garner Hook Junior High School

data.description: This charming home is loaded with upgrades and boasts an incredible open floor plan! The kitchen comes with all the finishes you desire – a complete suite of energy-efficient appliances, granite countertops, a spacious island, gorgeous wood cabinetry, recessed lighting and even USB outlets! On beautiful days, take the fun outside on your covered patio! You’ll also love the serene master suite, complete with a large window, spacious walk-in-closet and private attached bath.
